headline: Ovintiv Q4 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Decline Y/Y
summary: OVV tops Q4 earnings estimates as production climbs, but revenues slip year over year amid weaker oil prices.

headline: Targa Resources price target raised to $262 from $200 at Citi
summary: Citi analyst Spiro Dounis raised the firm’s price target on Targa Resources (TRGP) to $262 from $200 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares.
